ld 音乐节</a>，该音乐节将于四月返回拉斯维加斯。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/linkin-park">Linkin Park</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/metallica">Metallica</a>名列前茅，其他还有<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/evanescence">Evanence</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/queens-of-the-stone-age">Queens Of The Stone Age</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gojira">Gojira</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/afi">AFI</a>等。</p><p> 10月，Coyne还向<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-flaming-lips-collaborator-nell-smith-has-died-aged-17-3800422">17岁在加拿大因车祸去世的</a>前Flaming Lips合作者<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/flaming-lips-wayne-coyne-pays-tribute-after-death-dearest-amazing-beautiful-young-friend-nell-smith-3801263">Nell Smith表示敬意</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-flaming-lips-wayne-coyne-sharing-joint-paul-mccartney-entourage-3820148">《Flaming Lips》乐队的韦恩·科因 (Wayne Coyne) 在与保罗·麦卡特尼 (Paul McCartney) 合作时发表了这样的帖子：“他认为我是他的随从之一”，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
