loads/2024/12/the_rolling_stones-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-rolling-stones">滚石乐队</a>宣布了 2023 年专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-rolling-stones-hackney-diamonds-review-lyrics-tracklist-3515754">Hackney Diamonds</a> 》重新发行特别版的详细信息。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="753" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-rolling-stones-hackney-diamonds-review-lyrics-tracklist-3515754"><b>滚石乐队 - “哈克尼钻石”评论：他们仍然拥有它</b></a></li></ul><p>这支标志性乐队于去年 10 月发行了他们的第 24 张录音室专辑，这是他们自 2005 年的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-the-rolling-stones-7763-312997">A Bigger Bang</a> 》以来的第一张新专辑。其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lady-gaga">Lady Gaga</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/elton-john">埃尔顿·约翰</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paul-mccartney">保罗·麦卡特尼</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/stevie-wonder">史蒂夫·旺德</a>的客串演出，并收录了乐队已故鼓手<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charlie-watts">查理·沃茨</a>的最后一张唱片。</p><p>现在，新的“透明蓝色飞溅”黑胶双LP版本已经推出，以纪念其发行一周年，其中增加了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-rolling-stones-perform-with-lady-gaga-at-surprise-new-york-show-3518629">去年十月在纽约举行的唱片发布会上的七张现场录音</a>，其中包括“Sweet”与 Gaga 合作的《天籁之音》。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> Hackney Diamonds 周年纪念版现已与特别周年纪念周边商品一起推出。购买 2LP 泼墨黑胶唱片和 CD，包括纽约 Racket 现场演出！ <a href="https://t.co/mWsz7FAyrS">https://t.co/mWsz7FAyrS</a> <a href="https://t.co/ABuhpJiLFn">pic.twitter.com/ABuhpJiLFn</a></p><p> — 滚石乐队 (@RollingStones) <a href="https://twitter.com/RollingStones/status/1864965506463043783?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 12 月 6 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p> “哈克尼钻石（周年纪念版）”于周五（12 月 6 日）发布，您可以<a href="https://therollingstonesshop.co.uk/products/the-rolling-stones-hackney-diamonds-anniversary-edition" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>购买。完整曲目列表为： </p><ol><li data-leveltext="%1." data-font="" data-listid="754" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335551671&quot;:1,&quot;335552541&quot;:0,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769242&quot;:[65533,0,46],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;%1.&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"> <strong>&#39;生气的&#39;</strong> </li><li data-leveltext="%1." data-font="" data-listid="754" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335551671&quot;:1,&quot;335552541&quot;:0,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769242&quot;:[65533,0,46],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;%1.&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"> <strong>“靠近”</strong> </li><li data-leveltext="%1." data-font="" data-listid="754" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335551671&quot;:1,&quot;335552541&quot;:0,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769242&quot;:[65533,0,46],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;%1.&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"> <strong>“取决于你”</strong> </li><li data-leveltext="%1." data-font="" data-listid="754" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;